Interface UgcNodeIndexerExtension

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractUgcNodeIndexerExtension
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface UgcNodeIndexerExtension
    Interface class for extension of node indexing. Service implementations of this interface are no longer honored as of AEM 6.1
